

-- Check node version

  node -v
  v9.10.1

-- Execute a javascript using server-side runtime #6_16

  node test/test_helper.js

-- Run test suite in a node project

  npm run test #6_20

  Note:
    1.  Apart from the test script, any helper javascript code also gets executed 
        ( example; test_helper.json in users project)
   
    2.  In order to run the test, we have to set mocha for the `test` script in package.json
          Do not specify in single quote
        "scripts": {
          "test": "mocha"
        }

